---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = "Atermicos Pinamar - Caso de Éxito | Algoritmia";
const description = "Expansión geográfica y generación de leads High-Ticket mediante publicidad digital.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="bg-white text-black selection:bg-gray-200">
    <section class="relative pt-32 md:pt-48 pb-20 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wide">Caso de Éxito</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight text-black mb-8">
              5-10 leads/semana con publicidad digital.
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Implementamos campañas de publicidad en Meta Ads, generando un flujo constante de nuevos clientes potenciales cada mes.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 items-start lg:items-center">
              <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
                Ver Instagram
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_outward</span>
              </a>

              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100">
                <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">5-10</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium">Leads Mensuales</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex-1 w-full">
           <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 bg-black shadow-2xl shadow-gray-200/50 group">
              <!-- Testimonial Video -->
              <video 
                id="hero-testimonial-video"
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                controls
                poster=""
              >
                <source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfixkx6yi/video/upload/v1769687828/WhatsApp_Video_2026-01-28_at_5.57.05_PM_fpwrmp.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Tu navegador no soporta videos HTML5.
              </video>
            </div>


          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-gray-50 relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-black leading-tight max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          "Fabricamos bordes de piscina de alta calidad, pero vendemos poco. Queremos duplicar las ventas en 6 meses, aprovechando la temporada alta."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-6 font-medium">— El Desafío & Expectativa</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-black">Lo que hicimos</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg">Estrategia intensiva de captación de clientes sin necesidad de sitio web complejo.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">ads_click</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Meta Ads - Prospecting</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Segmentación avanzada para captar demanda activa de personas interesadas en piscinas y construcción.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">campaign</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Meta Ads - Retargeting</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Campañas para mantener la marca presente y captar clientes en fase de consideración.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">photo_camera</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Contenido de Obra</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Fotografías profesionales de obras terminadas para mostrar calidad y generar confianza en clientes potenciales.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 4 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">location_on</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Expansión Geográfica</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Segmentación de anuncios para captar clientes en zonas cercanas y expandir el radio de acción del negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black">Resultados Reales</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg">
              Los números no mienten.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider">Situación Inicial</p>
                <div class="flex items-end gap-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-400">Sin Publicidad</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-1">(Venta Pasiva)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-black shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-xs text-black uppercase mb-2 font-bold tracking-wider">Ahora</p>
                <div class="flex items-end gap-4">
                  <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-black">5-10</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">Leads/semanal</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-green-600 font-medium mt-2 text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">trending_up</span>
                  Proyectos High-Ticket
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-4">
              <p class="text-7xl font-bold text-black tracking-tighter">
                Temporada
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2 text-xl font-medium">Asegurada con obras cerradas</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative h-[400px] bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-xl shadow-gray-200/50 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-8 left-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black">Generación de Demanda</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Consultas Mensuales Promedio</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-end justify-center gap-12 h-[200px] w-full px-8">
              <div class="w-24 bg-gray-100 rounded-t-lg h-[10%] relative group flex justify-center">
                 <div class="absolute -top-8 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400">0-1</div>
                 <div class="absolute -bottom-8 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Orgánico</div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="w-24 bg-black rounded-t-lg h-[90%] relative group flex justify-center shadow-lg">
                 <div class="absolute -top-8 text-xl font-bold text-black">10+</div>
                 <div class="absolute -bottom-8 text-sm text-black font-bold">Con Ads</div>
                 
                 <div class="absolute top-4 w-full border-t border-white/30"></div>
                 <div class="absolute top-8 w-full border-t border-white/30"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-200 mt-10"></div>
             <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-4">Comparativa Mes 0 vs Mes 2</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 text-center bg-black text-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">¿Tu negocio necesita vender más?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-10">
          Creamos sistemas de ventas predecibles, incluso si no tienes sitio web.
        </p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          Solicitar Presupuesto
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>